{layout '@layout.latte'}
{var $active = 'overview'}

{block #title}{$config->title ?: 'Overview'}{/block}

{block #content}
<div id="content">
	<h1>{$config->title}</h1>

	<p>A long time ago, in a galaxy far far awayâ€¦ there has been an IT company called Jyxo s.r.o. It has existed for several years and created and contributed to numerous projects.</p>
	<p>To share fruits of work of individual project teams and to not re-invent the wheel over and over again, a collection of libraries has been created. It has been given the name "Jyxo PHP Library" and it has happily grown throughout the years.</p>
	<p>In <a href="https://github.com/jyxo">our repositories</a> we will continuously publish various bits and pieces from this library. We will do our best to publish everything that would be useful to anyone from the outside world. A big part of the library will also be covered by PHPUnit tests.</p>
	<p>Please read the license before using anything from this library.</p>
	<p>The library is published in two versions:</p>
	<ul>
		<li><a href="https://github.com/jyxo/php">With namespaces</a> (<a href="https://github.com/jyxo/php/blob/master/license.txt">license</a>, <a href="http://jyxo.github.com/php/">documentation</a>).</li>
		<li><a href="https://github.com/jyxo/php-no-namespace">Without namespaces</a> (<a href="https://github.com/jyxo/php-no-namespace/blob/master/license.txt">license</a>, <a href="http://jyxo.github.com/php-no-namespace/">documentation</a>).</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Overview</h3>

	{var $group = false}

	{if}
	<table class="summary" id="packages">
	<caption>Packages summary</caption>
	{foreach $packages as $package}
	{continueIf $config->main && 0 !== strpos($package, $config->main)}
	<tr>
		{var $group = true}
		<td><a href="{$package|packageUrl}">{$package}</a></td>
	</tr>
	{/foreach}
	</table>
	{/if $iterations}

	{if}
	<table class="summary" id="namespaces">
	<caption>Namespaces summary</caption>
	{foreach $namespaces as $namespace}
	{continueIf $config->main && 0 !== strpos($namespace, $config->main)}
	<tr>
		{var $group = true}
		<td><a href="{$namespace|namespaceUrl}">{$namespace}</a></td>
	</tr>
	{/foreach}
	</table>
	{/if $iterations}

	{if !$group}
	{include '@elementlist.latte'}
	{/if}
</div>
{/block}